p-group.p:
The Arab League participates in the International Support Group (ISG) for Lebanon (see under 
UNSCOL
) which was established by the UN Secretary-General in September 2013, and also comprises representatives of the UN, EU, People’s Republic of China, France, Germany, Italy, Russia, UK and USA.

